<BR>
<EM>
When sorrow draws near,<BR>
Wasted lies the gardens of the soul,<BR>
Withered and dying are joy and song.<BR>
Dark is life, is death.<BR>
</EM>
<BR>
(English translation by Deryck Cooke)<BR>
